indimail (@version@-4) unstable; urgency=low

  * moved qmail-newmrh, qmail-remote, qmail-newu, qmail-cdb to sbin
  * changed data type to TIMESTAMP from DATETIME for timestamp column in hostcntrl, lastauth
  * updated flash menu for changes in program paths in indimail-mta
  * svctool - inlookup supervise/control fifo - allow svc -h permission for vdeluser POST_HANDLE script
  * svctool - updated sql-mode in mysqld run file
  * svctool - refactored code for MySQL db creation
  * svctool - use .mylogin.cnf created by mysql_config_editor
  * use /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock.tmp as socket for mysqldb creation
  * svctool - use mysqld --verbose --check to check existence of a command line option
  * restrict userinfo privilege to root, indimail user/group
  * restrict userinfo privilege to root, indimail user/group
  * use configure.ac to use mysql_optionsv(), if available, instead of mysql_options()
  * svctool - inlookup service creation, activeDays default set to 7 days
  * create ld.so cache for indimail only when libdir is not /usr/lib or /usr/lib64
  * set_mysql_options.c - set MySQL options for SSL/TLS connections
  * added error_mysql_options_str() function to display the exact mysql_option() error
  * svctool - added --ssl, --require-secure-transport command line option for mysqld
  * use mysql_real_escape_string only if ENABLE_MYSQL_ESCAPE env variable is defined
  * svctool - added SSL/TLS paramters for MySQL service, config
  * ProcessInFifo.c - avoid connection to hostcntrl if host.cntrl is absent
  * set_mysql_option.c - use mysql_ssl_set() to fix ssl/tls connection issue when using libmariadb
  * fixed ambiguous select statement in join statement with timestamp column in indimail, lastuath table
  * set use_ssl paramter for MySQL connnections
  * added ability to use SSL/TLS encryption for MySQL connections. set use_ssl paramter for MySQL connnections
  * mysql_options() in libmariadb is unable to locate cnf files without an absolute path
  * LoadDbInfo.c - set mysql_socket for local dbinfo structure
  * dbload.c - pass socket argument to mysql_real_connect() to prevent failure for local connect with libmariadbclient
  * vauth_open.c, dbload.c - use local interface only when mysql socket is defined in host.mysql
  * vuserinfo, dbinfo - display SSL Cipher when use_ssl is set
  * use full path of cnf file for libmariadbclient bug
  * svctool - fix creation of env variable VIRTUAL_PKG_LIB
  * svctool - create SSL/TLS config for MariaDB like mysql_ssl_rsa_setup utility for mysql-community-server
  * svctool - autofix QHPSI during clamd service creation for smtpd, qmqpd, qmtpd
  * svctool - skip service refresh if .norefreshsvc file is present in variables directory
  * svctool - added --config=sqlssl for creating SSL/TLS config for mariadb

